divs: Sighting Details My son brought this bright light to my attentionin the sky. It looked like a large star. Colorful. Not moving. I looked at itwith binoculars and could see many different colors. Greens, blues, orange, red.We watched for about 20 minutes. Eventually moved slightly north, thendisappeared.
